'''同意投票黨'''（{{lang-en|Approval Voting Party}}，簡稱AVP）是美國一個致力於實施[[同意投票|同意投票]]的[[單一問題政治|單一議題]]政黨<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.coloradopolitics.com/news/colorados-approval-voting-party-achieves-minor-party-status/article_220466ac-e54b-11e9-bcd5-63add41f27e9.html|title=Colorado's Approval Voting Party achieves minor party status|website=Colorado Politics|last1=Luning|first1=Ernst|date=October 2, 2019|accessdate=August 8, 2020|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200820011635/https://www.coloradopolitics.com/news/colorados-approval-voting-party-achieves-minor-party-status/article_220466ac-e54b-11e9-bcd5-63add41f27e9.html|archive-date=2020-08-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2019年時該黨是科羅拉多州的一個小黨。

==歷史==
[[File:Frank_Atwood.jpg|thumb]]

同意投票黨由布萊克·胡伯與弗蘭克·阿特伍德聯合創立<ref name=West>{{cite web|url=https://www.westword.com/news/approval-voting-party-now-minor-party-in-colorado-11512652|title=Approval Voting Party Gains Minor Party Status — But It Doesn't Want Your Votes|website=Westword|last1=Fleming|first1=Sara|date=October 15, 2019|accessdate=August 8, 2020|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200820011149/https://www.westword.com/news/approval-voting-party-now-minor-party-in-colorado-11512652|archive-date=2020-08-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾在2018年提名胡伯競逐{{le|科羅拉多州務卿|Secretary of State of Colorado}}職務<ref name=Wants>{{cite web|url=http://ballot-access.org/2018/09/05/approval-voting-party-hopes-to-become-ballot-qualified-in-colorado/|title=Approval Voting Party Hopes to Become Ballot-Qualified in Colorado|website=Ballot Access News|last1=Winger|first1=Richard|date=September 5, 2018|accessdate=August 8, 2020|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112014904/http://ballot-access.org/2018/09/05/approval-voting-party-hopes-to-become-ballot-qualified-in-colorado/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於次年10月擁有超過1,000名註冊黨員，達到[[科羅拉多州|科羅拉多州]]小黨地位的要求<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ballot-access.org/2019/10/04/approval-voting-party-becomes-ballot-qualified-in-colorado/|title=Approval Voting Party Becomes Ballot-Qualified in Colorado|website=Ballot Access News|last1=Winger|first1=Richard|date=October 4, 2019|accessdate=August 8, 2020|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200820011635/https://www.coloradopolitics.com/news/colorados-approval-voting-party-achieves-minor-party-status/article_220466ac-e54b-11e9-bcd5-63add41f27e9.html|archive-date=2020-08-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年，[[利特尔顿_(科罗拉多州)|科罗拉多州利特尔顿]]選舉委員會委員阿特伍德試圖提出在該地區的無黨派市政選舉使用同意投票制度，選舉委員會投票決定將該措施交與市議會表決，但市議會以4票對3票否決<ref name=Littleton>{{cite web|url=https://littletonindependent.net/stories/making-a-case-for-a-different-way-to-vote,287219|title=Making a case for a different way to vote|website=Littleton Independent|last1=Gilbert|first1=David|date=October 4, 2019|accessdate=August 8, 2020|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200820010426/https://littletonindependent.net/stories/making-a-case-for-a-different-way-to-vote,287219|archive-date=2020-08-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

